data.description: Classic American Homes, THE LIBERTY, Plan A3284S. A beautiful 2-story home with 4 bedrooms and a loft, all upstairs, 2.5 baths, a large open concept, ideal for entertainment, granite counter tops, a large island in the kitchen with room for bar stools, refrigerated A/C, ceramic tile on the entire first floor, and much more. This is a new floor plan with rear-entrance 3-car garage. Pictures are of a proposed home.
